If you look down at the area below the   ^*bStep > ^*n   and   ^*bFlow^*n   buttons you will see the 'Navigation Bar'.  It has bumps on it labelled @-  'B', 'Str1' and 'Str2' etc.  The first bump shows the at beginning of the file, while the others show where a  ^*b!qx!<qx_label>!^*n  command has been put.|
