In large lin files with a lot of !qx! commands they show in two different ways.  

The !qx!'s that have a lot of !pg!'s following them show exactly (see the nav bar below) as do the ones we have here.  

Others, that have very few !pg!'s, show as narrow spikes not as wide bumps.  All are still clickable.

